item.title: New Website, AGM Results and Other Miscellaneous Updates!
item.description:
Welcome to the new website!

Hello Everyone, Welcome to the new Leeds Hacking Society Website. We have been busy over Summer rebranding and putting everything together ready for the new term. We hope you like it!

If you are interested in our Society or wish to contact us, please feel free to message us on the Facebook page or drop us an Email.
